8.ezboard.com/bmonklybusiness43508.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=anezka>Anezka</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www3.sympatico.ca/pratte1/Icone.bmp" BORDER=0> at: 5/3/02 9:54:05 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/uturrun.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Turrun</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(3/7/01 11:21:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=199.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> RE:  Factions...</span><hr size=1> I highly recommend this walkthrough!  So far, it's great!  I would clarify one minor detail in that you can get to the dark rogue in the East Freeport Tunnels without risking the main city.  There are entrances to the tunnels at both the East and West Freeport gates.<br><br>I also have one related question: Does anyone know what the going price is to get wolform cast on you?  I have made a few requests offering &quot;donation&quot; but have had no takers yet. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/bmonklybusiness43508.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=anezka>Anezka</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://fp.geocities.com/hazea2000/Icone.bmp BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Disciple</span><br>  Posts: 144<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(3/8/01 8:38:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=199.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Here's the direct link</span><hr size=1> I have no idea what the going price for wolf form is, on both times I had to get one, I went in EC, found a druid not anon and offered him 